sts, neonatal nurse practitioners, registered nurses, developmental therapists, lactation consultants, respiratory therapists, and social workers, provide 24/7 care for infants born prematurely, with low birth weights, congenital birth defects, and unanticipated complications during delivery.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HSHS St. Vincent Children's Hospital's NICU is labeled as the first, largest, and longest-serving NICU in the Green Bay region.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_van_Gogh\", \"score\": 0.9968514901196769, \"rank\": 0.0031041229296327856, \"text\": \"Vincent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_van_Gogh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincent_van_Gogh\"}, {\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neonatal_intensive_care_unit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NICU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neonatal_intensive_care_unit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neonatal_intensive_care_unit\"}, {\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neonatal_intensive_care_unit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NICU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neonatal_intensive_care_unit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neonatal_intensive_care_unit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 WBAY.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": []}]}"